high_descs: Go around the island to the fridge ahead, turn right, turn right to face the counter to the right of the sink.
Take the large knife next to the tomato.
Turn around, go to the counter to the left of the oven.
Cut the bread into slices.
Stay at the counter.
Put the knife on the counter between the fork and the edge of the counter.
Stay at the counter.
Take a piece of bread from the counter.
Turn left, go to the refrigerator on the right.
Put the bread in the fridge next to the plate and bowl. Close then open the fridge door. Take the bread from the fridge.
Turn right, go to the oven on the left.
Put the bread in the microwave above the oven.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of bread in a microwave.

high_descs: Turn left and begin walking to the door, then turn right and walk to the fridge, then hang a right and walk up to the knives on the kitchen island.
Pick up the left most metal knife with a golden handle.
Turn left and walk over to the loaf of bread on the kitchen counter.
Slice the loaf of bread with the metal knife.
Turn left and take a step forward, then turn right to face the kitchen counter.
Place the metal knife onto the kitchen counter in front of the fork.
Turn right, take a step forward then face left so you are facing the sliced bread on the kitchen counter..
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn left and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the sliced bread inside, then close the door and wait a few seconds, after that open the fridge door back up and remove the slice of bread and close the door again.
Turn right and walk over to the stove, then look up at the microwave in the upper cabinets.
Open the microwave door, place the slice of bread inside, then close the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled slice of bread into the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left, take a step, then turn right towards the fridge, and then turn right towards the counter on your right.
Pick up the left yellow knife from the counter.
Turn around and head towards the loaf of bread on the counter.
Slice the bread into slices.
Take a step to the left.
Place the knife in front of the fork on the counter.
Take a step to the right.
Pick up a slice of bread from the counter.
Turn left and head towards the fridge on your right.
Open the fridge, place the slice bread in between the bowl and plate, close the fridge to let it cool down, and then take the bread back out.
Turn right, walk towards the stove on your left, and look up to find a microwave.
Open the microwave, place the slice bread in it, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a cool slice of bread in the microwave.
